an style=\"color: gold;\">迎接未來</span><br />\n<br />\n短期目標：改善抗爭能力，提升身份認同<br />\n建議：文宣！各有各做，best effort <br />\n中期目標：區議會(94%民主產生)<br />\n建議：關注身邊人，團結一致，各有各做<br />\n長期目標：強化黃色陣營、民主/黃色經濟圈<br />\n建議：抗爭生活化，減少比錢極權陣營<br />\n終極目標：民選議會、民選政府<br />\n建議：國際戰線、傳播思想、滲透內部<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公務員</span></strong>：小隱於野，中隱於市，大隱於朝<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和勇合一</strong></span>：1.合法之下，最大勇武<br />\n                     2. 做任何事，永不被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">@謠言係疫症&bull;不傳播&bull;去求診&bull;澄清藥<br />\n@FakeNews係Cancer&bull;不擴散&bull;求事實&bull;割<br />\n@接觸資訊時，腦袋要清醒</span><br />\n<br />\n只要爭取民主團火未熄，還是有機會達成<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">衛城革命，生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡，打倒腐敗</span><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\n<strong><em>升級技能/能力值</em></strong>：1. 讀書、識法律2.運動、鬥長命3.和勇合一精神4.批判性思考5.精通專業技能<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMdiioB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMdiioB.jpg&h=7e10cb33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=pX%2F9NM0RDLHEoMpKo%2B7ToRZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=0ff79b3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n理非可以做的事<a href=\"https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTakeActionWithYou&d=pX%2F9NM0RDLHEoMpKo%2B7ToRZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=599a4326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou</a><br />\n良心與無良商戶<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2F&d=pX%2F9NM0RDLHEoMpKo%2B7ToRZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=77a83283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/</a><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\nVersion 2019.10.04<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">要記住極權如何打壓香港示威：</span></strong><br />\n1.抹黑：利用少部分的暴力衝突而將全部示威者形容為「邪惡」、示威=港獨、新華社、環球時報、人民日報<br />\n2.誤導：警總救護車、雷射槍、9吋尖刀等等<br />\n3.滲透：5毛、陳雲、黃x民、譚香文<br />\n4.假民意/曲解民意：主流民意是......<br />\n5.5毛輿論-分化、負面、fake news、煽動手足做負效益/低效益工作<br />\n6.強迫企業自我審查<br />\n7.出動黑社會、愛國暴徒<br />\n8.扮示威者：(負面的)破壞eg.遊行<br />\n9.嫁禍示威者/黑警：打議員打記者打女仔<br />\n10.扮好人/扮對話：「江山易改本性難移」<br />\n11.警察濫權、濫捕、暴力執法、恐嚇<br />\n12.利用親中人士發表「假」權威言論<br />\n13.用盡手段打壓反對聲音<br />\n14.矮化示威者為甲由、yellow object<br />\n諗到再加</span><br />\nVictory at all costs, victory in spite of all terror, victory however long and hard the road may be; for without victory, there is no survival.<br />\nWinston Churchill"},{"pid":"a32ede47c902aa36632db9e2875c568b7cf90693","tid":1619442,"uid":120243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:17:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3690e09c2b0a0f9d970fe34f79c36073d33cfd2a","tid":1619442,"uid":161025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:18:43.000Z","msg":"所有外國戰線都要推 林奠不停重重複咁講唔係緊急狀態 睇黎有野驚"},{"pid":"4e8fd428b249fb42df855e5a739e8eb8e90ccb5f","tid":1619442,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:20:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2b4ed51c32faa97124e79c806677c179220bf459","tid":1619442,"uid":205275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3690e09c2b0a0f9d970fe34f79c36073d33cfd2a","tid":1619442,"uid":161025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:18:43.000Z","msg":"所有外國戰線都要推 林奠不停重重複咁講唔係緊急狀態 睇黎有野驚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:22:03.000Z","msg":"條仆街咁鍾意用語言偽術 佢話唔係咁即係係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同我推上twitter熱門！！！"},{"pid":"d6e5f1bf66b20a1bf55c5b9e84375ced264c3d56","tid":1619442,"uid":289441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"