槍謀殺義士！我地一定要立即制止納粹警暴歪風！請大家立即籌備無限期罷工、罷課！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請文宣幫手將以上論點製作poster廣傳，多謝各位</strong>"},{"pid":"60858f3b1296c62f58f4189b46047ffe72bcbd77","tid":1619442,"uid":60872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:30:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81baf1eef07c6fec744245dcb96c205f927dacbf","tid":1619442,"uid":112393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:30:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7e9b6821ffee621e5f51a4a3d41d671c294ac15","tid":1619442,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bf96e3bf8b93cb533610f17cc7b1c774b818b78","tid":1619442,"uid":261478,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:59:40.000Z","msg":"宣佈成立臨時政府<br />\n再立即宣佈香港進入戰爭狀態<br />\n同時以臨時政府名義請求聯合國出兵<br />\n並承諾香港將承擔所有戰爭開支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:31:42.000Z","msg":"得唔得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊個帶頭呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf24d612eb602c81fc0e36df200eab28a2683d6b","tid":1619442,"uid":109544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:32:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8a9e822b3afc74f839d7f99a8886375ad9a6d2f","tid":1619442,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6038a568946c1c825283e6fa36ed2103db01eb","tid":1619442,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:33:56.000Z","msg":"我都想係真，但有無理據支持？"},{"pid":"025b67934503b2ac46ac5c74c41ef8c0730b001f","tid":1619442,"uid":242863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.g